.TH "set_phyerrthreshold" 9 "set_phyerrthreshold" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
set_phyerrthreshold \- set the physical error threshold
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" set_phyerrthreshold
.BI "(struct qib_pportdata *ppd "  ","
.BI "unsigned n "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ppd" 12
the physical port data
.IP "n" 12
the new threshold
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Note that this will only take effect when the link state changes.
